{"tid":623412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港FIFA 比賽冠,亞軍毒撚都係用狗隊","createTime":"2018-04-10T03:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T11:04:30.000Z","uid":106204,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4b37640cdfe251e1f3b698e71c6f321c531f9f34","tid":623412,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:40:20.000Z","msg":"作為香港體壇盛事，香港國際七人欖球賽又豈止欖球賽這麼簡單，在銅鑼灣希慎廣場就有七欖配套活動的電競比賽同步進行，讓大家感受七欖氣氛之餘，同時認識電競，而周日（4月8日）的《FIFA 18》決賽就有李嘉俊（Jesus）於用皇家馬德里以2：1擊敗Wayne操作的曼聯，贏得一萬元獎金。<br />\n<br />\n於70分鐘以2：0領先的Jesus看似勝利在望，但當Wayne換上「全攻陣」頓時令他感到緊張，Wayne更於90分鐘攻入一球追成2：1，惜為時以晚，Jesus以一球之微險勝對手。對於經常以皇家馬德里應戰，Jesus表示：「皇馬是遊戲中較強的隊伍，而且自己經常都留意皇馬的比賽。」除了在遊戲中較強勢，還有一個令Jesus選用皇馬：「因為有C朗拿度！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然同為《FIFA 18》玩家，但Jesus就指在家享受與出外比賽感受大為不同，即使曾到國外出賽，他都會因環境氣氛令心情變得緊張，影響表現。當提起出國經驗，Jesus更是侃侃而談：「去年曾到過澳洲、加拿大及卡塔爾出賽，要取得資格並不容易，要先在家玩Full Champion模式打進地區性前16名，就會獲EA官方邀請參賽。」Jesus大讚EA安排周到，重視選手之餘獎金亦同樣豐富。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2018/04/20180408_fifa_2_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2018%2F04%2F20180408_fifa_2_up.jpg&h=bc15f563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2018/04/20180408_fifa_1_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2018%2F04%2F20180408_fifa_1_up.jpg&h=25f79362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2018/04/20180408_fifa_4_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2018%2F04%2F20180408_fifa_4_up.jpg&h=54a03f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2018/04/20180408_fifa_3_up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2018%2F04%2F20180408_fifa_3_up.jpg&h=7d9b2aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc77c3ef5feb906ac47f2a8ae3d44b8919e2266d","tid":623412,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1633290bf0cbad55d382d913f423a9cb2a0ab36b","tid":623412,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9648c2b581691ea8359c454ad79a4c61fab8f2fc","tid":623412,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc938da3b96dda2f971552d9c5608ce6b615f9c","tid":623412,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9576d196fdf129cacccb35c788da6fa056ba9a01","tid":623412,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"Wayne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1900ff9f84981eee66b31697b59b0f90b31196","tid":623412,"uid":33601,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"冠軍定亞軍用狗隊？定兩隊一齊用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400bbb61a96612be1ec2d783d41840a16772e5f3",